		<h2>List of contributions</h2>
		<ul>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2009/index.html">SLE 2009</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2009/paper19.html">Declarative Scripting in Haskell</a></em> (<a href="../profile/TimBauer.html">Tim Bauer</a>, <a href="../profile/MartinErwig.html"><span class="info">Martin Erwig</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2010/index.html">SLE 2010</a>)</span> <em>Authored <a href="../sle2010/keynote1.html">A Language for Software Variation Research</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MartinErwig.html"><span class="info">Martin Erwig</span></a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2011/index.html">SLE 2011</a>)</span> <em>Coauthored <a href="../sle2011/paper12.html">Semantics First! Rethinking the Language Design Process</a></em> (<a href="../profile/MartinErwig.html"><span class="info">Martin Erwig</span></a>, <a href="../profile/EricWalkingshaw.html">Eric Walkingshaw</a>) </li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2013/index.html">SLE 2013</a>)</span> Served as a <a href="https://www.sleconf.org/2013/Committees.html">Programme Chair</a></li>
<li><span class="info">(<a href="../sle2014/index.html">SLE 2014</a>)</span> Served on <a href="https://www.sleconf.org/2014/Committees.html">PC</a></li>
